title: Harlan Green Dragons play for District Champion Friday
text:
/ Headlines List / Article 
HARLAN, Ky. (WYMT) -- The Harlan-Pineville rivalry football game goes back to the 1920s. This Friday, the two meet again, with the Green Dragons trying to clinch the Class A, District 7 title. 
Harlan is on a three game win streak going into the game. 
"District championship is on the line for us Friday night and if we can win the game, we get a district championship and that's something we talk to our kids about since July and that's what you for and you try to get that one seed and give yourself a good seeding in the playoffs." 
For more on this game, check out the video above.
